title: Water Insecurity
text:
water_sec <- readr::read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/refs/heads/main/data/2025/2025-01-28/water_insecurity_2023.csv") 

library(ggplot2)



ggplot(water_sec, aes(x = percent_lacking_plumbing)) + 
  geom_histogram(fill = "purple", color = "black", bins = 30) + 
  facet_wrap(~ year) + 
  theme_light() + labs(title = "Histogram between Lack of Plumbing with Years", x = "Percentage")

title: The History of Himalayan Mountaineering Expeditions
text:
library(tidyverse)

mount <- readr::read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/refs/heads/main/data/2025/2025-01-21/peaks_tidy.csv")

ggplot(mount, aes(x = PYEAR, y = HEIGHTM, color = HEIGHTM )) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_line() + 
  labs(title = "Regression between Height & Exp. Year", x = "Year of Expedition", y = "Max Height in Meter")
